TI  - Quick Fix: How to Constructively Manage Cell Phone Misuse in the Classroom without Coercion or Score Pollution
PY  - 2025
JO  - College Teaching
DO  - 10.1080/87567555.2023.2245526
AB  - In this article, I describe how I spend only one minute per class to help students resist being distracted by their phones. © 2023 Taylor & Francis Group, LLC.
